  "body": "url: https://solidity.readthedocs.io/en/latest/common-patterns.html#withdrawal-pattern\r\ncodes with bug:\r\n```\r\nfunction becomeRichest() public payable returns (bool) {\r\n        if (msg.value > mostSent) {\r\n            pendingWithdrawals[richest] += msg.value;\r\n            richest = msg.sender;\r\n            mostSent = msg.value;\r\n            return true;\r\n        } else {\r\n            return false;\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n```\r\n\r\nI think the codes should be:\r\n```\r\nfunction becomeRichest() public payable returns (bool) {\r\n        pendingWithdrawals[msg.sender] += msg.value;\r\n        if (msg.value > mostSent) {\r\n            richest = msg.sender;\r\n            mostSent = msg.value;\r\n            return true;\r\n        } else {\r\n            return false;\r\n        }\r\n    }\r\n```",
